---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Create Issue Compatibility" description="Compatibility page pointing issue creation to the development board.">
<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url=/development-board#contribute" />
<section class="command-hero rounded-[2rem] border border-primary/20 bg-base-200 p-6 md:p-10 shadow-2xl"><p class="badge badge-primary badge-lg mb-4">Moved</p><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-4">Issue creation moved to the Development Board.</h1><p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-base-content/75">Per-repository bug, feature, docs, issue, PR, discussion, and wiki actions now live on the public development board.</p><a class="btn btn-primary mt-6" href="/development-board#contribute">Go to contribution actions</a></section>
</Layout>
